## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="23938-102">Nella tabella seguente vengono elencate le opzioni attualmente supportate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-102">The following table shows the currently supported options.</span></span>  
  
|<span data-ttu-id="23938-103">Category</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-103">Category</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-104">Impostazione</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-104">Setting</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-105">Valore/effetto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-105">Value/effect</span></span>|  
|--------------|-------------|-------------------|  
|<span data-ttu-id="23938-106">contratto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-106">contract</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-107">ereditarietà</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-107">inheritance</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-108">`true` per abilitare l'ereditarietà del contratto; `false` per disabilitarla.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-108">`true` to turn contract inheritance on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="23938-109">Il valore predefinito è `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-109">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
|<span data-ttu-id="23938-110">runtime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-110">runtime</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-111">controllo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-111">checking</span></span>|<span data-ttu-id="23938-112">`true` per abilitare il controllo runtime; `false` per disabilitarlo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-112">`true` to turn run-time checking on; `false` to turn it off.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="23938-113">Il valore predefinito è `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-113">The default is `true`.</span></span>|  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23938-114">È possibile utilizzare questo attributo come illustrato negli esempi seguenti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-114">You can use this attribute as illustrated in the following examples.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23938-115">Per disabilitare il controllo runtime per l'intero assembly:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-115">To turn off run-time checking for the entire assembly:</span></span>  
  
```  
[assembly:ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23938-116">Per abilitare il controllo runtime del contratto per un tipo specifico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-116">To turn run-time contract checking on for a specific type:</span></span>  
  
```  
   [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", true)]  
   class TypeWithRuntimeChecking {  
  
       ...  
  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="23938-117">Per disabilitare il controllo runtime per un metodo specifico:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="23938-117">To turn run-time checking off for a specific method:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Turn off all contract inheritance from interface IList<T>  
[ContractOption("contract", "inheritance", false)]  
class MyConcurrentList<T> : IList<T> {  
   ...  
}  
  
[ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
public override MyMethod(int x) {  
   // no inherited contracts checked at runtime,  
   // no invariants checked at runtime.  
   ...  
}  
  
       [ContractOption("runtime", "checking", false)]  
       public void MethodWithoutRuntimeChecking(...) {  
          ...  
       }  
   }  
  
```
